{"tid":1616960,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日和你DIN","createTime":"2019-10-03T15:00:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T11:44:36.000Z","uid":284319,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"b4887cc09bfa578e6f8a8d2a2f2920e75ab9c92c","tid":1616960,"uid":284319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T15:00:04.000Z","msg":"聽晚有和你din arrrr<br />\n<br />\n為左比大家更快 更清晰分到黃店<br />\n小妹同朋友整左個小黃衣Pepe logo <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rQfgK14.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrQfgK14.png&h=17291ac8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(唔好意思小妹無學畫畫到好似垃圾桶 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為咁易剪啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n希望係聽晚之前可以派比不同地區既黃店希望佢地可以貼係門口比大家睇<br />\n但人手有限未必聽日之前去到曬18區<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而派發的目標暫時以餐廳為主 名單係係之前巴打整既黃藍食肆到搵既黃店<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/d/u/0/viewer?mid=10SCYSkgC9KMC_kAGtLChlGRLWVbk8NTs&amp;ll=22.290765184207217%2C114.13904183549494&amp;z=17\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fmaps%2Fd%2Fu%2F0%2Fviewer%3Fmid%3D10SCYSkgC9KMC_kAGtLChlGRLWVbk8NTs%26ll%3D22.290765184207217%252C114.13904183549494%26z%3D17&d=Sqlr%2BNOTUp1GXDSzM%2FaCEn4HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=5fca54fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/maps/d/u/0/viewer?mid=10SCYSkgC9KMC_kAGtLChlGRLWVbk8NTs&amp;ll=22.290765184207217%2C114.13904183549494&amp;z=17</a><br />\n<br />\n每一隻pepe都有自己number架 希望大家可以支持下<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wEdewHF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwEdewHF.png&h=93d91e62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">時代革命</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19c80126f8d1cb53fd653d84fc8fec7979a34feb","tid":1616960,"uid":284319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T15:01:50.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc369be3caa4d288dec6144f7478dd30d4895298","tid":1616960,"uid":304834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T15:02:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc5b0314e2ca74fec5a93553e2827eb8def0f42f","tid":1616960,"uid":43925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T15:02:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"79d779f2bd394baa97d4fb9da2394a738bf69263","tid":1616960,"uid":42389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T15:02:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"55aef9eac6455b3664e0ac56ba31ffda01a6b48e","tid":1616960,"uid":13514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T15:02:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5958ccb0a5a8bead9cdcb2381f448628351dd3ea","tid":1616960,"uid":10630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T15:02:50.000Z","msg":"聽日早上九點半 沙田裁判法院聲援義士<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1616686\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1616686</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d37c646409fd327241936b70451027613e6b15c8","tid":1616960,"uid":12053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T15:03:36.000Z","msg":"好有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a